CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 9, 1957, pg. 3 combined with 2001.35.46087, reads: "'And the Join Rocked' - Fifteen hundred frenzied fans of Ray Charles turned 'Bill Powell's Big Birthday Ball' into 'Bill Powell's Big Birthday Brawl' at the Off-Shore Club, Blythedale, shown above. Direction sign appears on road short distance from dance spot. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Sign inscribed "Off Shore Club Dancing and Skating, Turn Here" on lawn with telephone pole and house on left, Blythedale, Pennsylvania
